Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Blocking from the outside with White 1 is the vital point to capture.
\par It is hard to find this kind of move during an actual game.
\par
\par Black has to connect at 2 and then White 3 is a good move so Black is dead.
\par }
