Dia. 02 Bend Four in the Corner
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par This is the proof of Black's death.
\par If Black plays, the only move is to capture with 1.
\par
\par After that White takes with 2.
